ss=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 од 5 звездица\" data-title-template=\"%s од 5 звездица\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Од <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stephenbishop/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f395cb3abb7590c46699e4f286cbbc1c83ebe63d6eddbb5c07ac1fe442bd8f31?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f395cb3abb7590c46699e4f286cbbc1c83ebe63d6eddbb5c07ac1fe442bd8f31?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stephenbishop/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">stephenbishop</a> <span class=\"review-date\">мај 15, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Absolutely terrible, and has been for years. I loathe working with WooCommerce. Outdated, buggy, and bloated. Sure it\'s free, but it is very expensive to add plugins and extensions to add the tiniest bit of extra functionality for things that frankly should be built-in. Customizing the templates is a hair-pulling experience by modifying endless filters and actions. Avoid if you can. Use SureCart instead, it is miles ahead.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 од 5 звездица\" data-title-template=\"%s од 5 звездица\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Од <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alfista/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f3ae264fa76427191f51802c661699a39755ec745e5e0524be0fbb9a040d407?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f3ae264fa76427191f51802c661699a39755ec745e5e0524be0fbb9a040d407?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alfista/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">alfista</a> <span class=\"review-date\">мај 15, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Its a good peace of plugin and its on good way to be better.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best plugin for simple shops</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 од 5 звездица\" data-title-template=\"%s од 5 звездица\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Од <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ultiblayz/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://se