iv class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Needed some help on a relatively simple issue, but I\'m not techie enough. Thanks for the quick support I received!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Una forma fácil para vender online</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 од 5 звездица\" data-title-template=\"%s од 5 звездица\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Од <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joegomrey/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3a20167e57a46844b5d416925b65c909b58cc78a27ce87ed59d8301719f7a9d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3a20167e57a46844b5d416925b65c909b58cc78a27ce87ed59d8301719f7a9d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joegomrey/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">joegomrey</a> <span class=\"review-date\">мај 15, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WooCommerce es de los plugins más fáciles de e-commerce que he usado, la guía al instalarlo me ayudo muchísimo, en general estoy bastante feliz con el.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Ahora tengo una tienda profesional sin complicaciones</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 од 5 звездица\" data-title-template=\"%s од 5 звездица\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Од <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cristiancalp23/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08c9c65a651d1ba1ab214a016daa55385a3ee860b3f8d705e37f6e96a7596995?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08c9c65a651d1ba1ab214a016daa55385a3ee860b3f8d705e37f6e96a7596995?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cristiancalp23/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Cristian <small>(cristiancalp23)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">мај 14, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Desde que instalé WooCommerce en mi web, vender productos se ha vuelto mucho más sencillo.<br />Me encanta lo fácil que es añadir nuevos artículos, gestionar los pedidos y ofrecer diferentes<br />métodos de pago a mis clientes. Las plantillas básicas son suficientes para mostrar bien mis<br />productos, y si necesito algo más, siempre encuentro plugins que amplían las posibilidades.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lo mejor es que todo funciona integrado en mi WordPress, sin complicaciones. Los clientes<br />pueden comprar de forma segura y yo tengo todo controlado desde el mismo panel. WooCommerce<br />ha sido justo lo que necesitaba para dar el salto y empezar a ve